   "source": [
    "import scipy\n",
    "from spafe.utils import vis\n",
    "from spafe.features.lfcc import lfcc\n",
    "\n",
    "# init input vars\n",
    "num_ceps = 13\n",
    "low_freq = 0\n",
    "high_freq = 2000\n",
    "nfilts = 24\n",
    "nfft = 512\n",
    "dct_type = 2,\n",
    "use_energy = False,\n",
    "lifter = 5\n",
    "normalize = False\n",
    "    \n",
    "# read wav \n",
    "fs, sig = scipy.io.wavfile.read(\"test.wav\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# compute features\n",
    "lfccs = lfcc(sig=sig,\n",
    "             fs=fs,\n",
    "             num_ceps=num_ceps,\n",
    "             nfilts=nfilts,\n",
    "             nfft=nfft,\n",
    "             low_freq=low_freq,\n",
    "             high_freq=high_freq,\n",
    "             dct_type=dct_type,\n",
    "             use_energy=use_energy,\n",
    "             lifter=lifter,\n",
    "             normalize=normalize)\n",
    "\n",
    "# visualize spectogram\n",
    "vis.spectogram(sig, fs)\n",
    "# visualize features\n",
    "vis.visualize_features(lfccs, 'LFCC Index', 'Frame Index')"
   ]
